WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.314 --> 00:00:02.015
In a quiet neighborhood in Qatar

2
00:00:02.215 --> 00:00:03.837
life moves peacefully.

3
00:00:04.037 --> 00:00:05.829
Homes glow with warm light.

4
00:00:06.205 --> 00:00:07.325
Families gather.

5
00:00:07.525 --> 00:00:09.239
This is a network

6
00:00:09.439 --> 00:00:11.743
a community where everyone’s connected

7
00:00:11.943 --> 00:00:13.565
where joy is shared,

8
00:00:13.765 --> 00:00:14.925
but also

9
00:00:15.125 --> 00:00:18.418
where danger can spread faster than anyone imagines.

10
00:00:19.229 --> 00:00:21.481
Two houses, two families,

11
00:00:21.681 --> 00:00:23.016
connected by friendship

12
00:00:23.514 --> 00:00:25.693
by proximity, by technology.

13
00:00:25.893 --> 00:00:26.797
Separate homes

14
00:00:26.997 --> 00:00:31.524
but linked through the invisible web of their network.

15
00:00:31.724 --> 00:00:33.023
Inside Hamad’s home

16
00:00:33.223 --> 00:00:35.884
father and son settle for the evening

17
00:00:36.084 --> 00:00:38.437
The big match is about to start.

18
00:00:38.637 --> 00:00:40.306
But there’s a problem.

19
00:00:40.506 --> 00:00:42.490
The channel isn’t working.

20
00:00:42.515 --> 00:00:44.088
Father flips through channels.

21
00:00:44.288 --> 00:00:44.857
Nothing

22
00:00:45.057 --> 00:00:46.033
Static

23
00:00:46.233 --> 00:00:47.255
Frustration

24
00:00:47.455 --> 00:00:50.685
Next door, Ali and his friend face the same problem

25
00:00:50.885 --> 00:00:52.709
No signal, no match

26
00:00:52.909 --> 00:00:55.699
just an empty screen and growing disappointment.

27
00:00:55.899 --> 00:01:00.586
Two households, same issue, both searching for a solution.

28
00:01:00.802 --> 00:01:01.612
Bing!

29
00:01:01.812 --> 00:01:03.053
Hamad’s phone lights up

30
00:01:03.253 --> 00:01:04.146
 A message

31
00:01:04.346 --> 00:01:05.081
a link

32
00:01:05.281 --> 00:01:07.404
 "free match streaming, watch now!"

33
00:01:07.604 --> 00:01:10.462
His eyes light up with excitement.

34
00:01:14.114 --> 00:01:15.348
Hamad clicks the link.

35
00:01:15.548 --> 00:01:17.522
The match appears on screen.

36
00:01:17.722 --> 00:01:18.481
Success

37
00:01:18.681 --> 00:01:19.629
Goals!

38
00:01:19.743 --> 00:01:20.605
Excitement!

39
00:01:20.805 --> 00:01:22.967
But what Hamad doesn’t know

40
00:01:23.167 --> 00:01:26.399
is that the link didn’t just bring the match

41
00:01:26.599 --> 00:01:28.349
It brought something else.

42
00:01:28.549 --> 00:01:31.470
A worm has entered their network

43
00:01:32.600 --> 00:01:34.610
Hamad forwards the link to Ali.

44
00:01:34.810 --> 00:01:36.441
One tap, one message 

45
00:01:36.641 --> 00:01:38.178
"check this out!"

46
00:01:38.771 --> 00:01:42.272
The worm has already started its work in Hamad’s house

47
00:01:42.472 --> 00:01:43.388
and now

48
00:01:43.588 --> 00:01:46.415
now it’s about to jump to the next network

49
00:01:46.957 --> 00:01:47.571
Suddenly

50
00:01:48.042 --> 00:01:48.902
flicker!

51
00:01:49.102 --> 00:01:51.344
Both TVs start glitching

52
00:01:51.544 --> 00:01:53.113
The match image distorts.

53
00:01:53.313 --> 00:01:55.924
Next door, Ali sees the same thing

54
00:01:56.124 --> 00:01:57.145
Is it the link?

55
00:01:57.345 --> 00:01:58.687
But it’s too late.

56
00:01:58.887 --> 00:02:00.889
The worm is executing its code.

57
00:02:01.089 --> 00:02:04.420
“The AC! It’s turning on and off by itself!"

58
00:02:04.620 --> 00:02:07.883
"The TV! It’s flickering wildly!”

59
00:02:08.786 --> 00:02:12.153
Two separate homes, two separate local networks

60
00:02:12.353 --> 00:02:15.110
but the same malware is attacking both.

61
00:02:15.310 --> 00:02:17.283
But it doesn’t stop there

62
00:02:17.483 --> 00:02:19.362
The worm has found the router

63
00:02:19.562 --> 00:02:21.769
the gateway to the wider network

64
00:02:21.969 --> 00:02:25.834
It explodes outward like wildfire through the neighborhood. 

65
00:02:26.034 --> 00:02:27.659
House after house

66
00:02:27.859 --> 00:02:29.320
screen after screen

67
00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:31.152
device after device

68
00:02:31.352 --> 00:02:34.407
The entire neighborhood’s network is infected

69
00:02:34.607 --> 00:02:36.849
This is the terrifying power of a worm

70
00:02:37.049 --> 00:02:39.168
It doesn’t need you to spread

71
00:02:39.368 --> 00:02:41.268
It spreads by itself.

72
00:02:42.043 --> 00:02:44.179
Hamad’s father springs into action

73
00:02:44.379 --> 00:02:45.932
“Unplug everything!”

74
00:02:46.132 --> 00:02:48.491
He yanks cables from the router 

75
00:02:48.691 --> 00:02:50.229
pulls the TV plug

76
00:02:50.429 --> 00:02:52.723
disconnects devices one by one

77
00:02:52.923 --> 00:02:55.454
This is emergency containment

78
00:02:55.654 --> 00:02:56.939
When a worm attacks,

79
00:02:57.139 --> 00:03:00.089
sometimes the only way to stop it

80
00:03:00.289 --> 00:03:03.689
is to physically disconnect from the network.

81
00:03:03.889 --> 00:03:05.552
Ali shuts down the AC

82
00:03:05.752 --> 00:03:09.700
but the damage is spreading faster than they can stop it

83
00:03:10.286 --> 00:03:12.035
The neighborhood goes dark.

84
00:03:12.235 --> 00:03:13.847
Devices unplugged

85
00:03:14.047 --> 00:03:15.694
networks shut down

86
00:03:15.894 --> 00:03:17.942
The worm has been stopped.

